This paper deals with the use of deep neural networks as controllers for dynamical systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of reachability methods and neural network verification tools, which are commonly used in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, and cs.NE.
